@node gads "Gadgets & contrôles clavier"
@Prev Usage
@Next Prefs
@Toc Main



                      @{u}@{b}L'interface utilisateur@{ub}@{uu}

   ------------------------------------------------------
   | -------------------------------------------------- |
   | |@{"Modinfo/Scope" link modinfoscope}                                   | |
   | -------------------------------------------------- |
